OL,6,FAn fan has been jailed for 15 weeks
OL,7,Fand handed a six-year stadium ban
OL,8,Fafter posting racist abuse online.
OL,10,FShaun Tuck, from , wrote the racist
OL,11,Fcomments about a fellow Everton
OL,12,Fsupporter in the comments section of
OL,13,FEverton's official Facebook page in
OL,14,FAugust 2023.
OL,16,FHe was found guilty of malicious
OL,17,Fcommunications and was sentenced at
OL,18,FSouth Sefton Magistrates Court on 29
OL,19,FFebruary.
